Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Gomersal in Birkenshaw 
    Urban District. Abolished 1.4.1937 and added to the parish of Gomersal.

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Gomersal in Birstall 
    Urban District. Abolished 1.4.1937 and added to the parish of Batley.

Abolished 1.4.1937 and added to the parish of Churwell. See 
    also Table 2, note (e).
Abolished 1.4.1974 and added to the Kirklees unparished area.

Abolished 1.4.1937 and added to the parish of Morley. See 
    also Table 2, note (d).

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Mirfield in Ravensthorpe 
    Urban District. Abolished 1.4.1925 and added to the parish of Dewsbury.

Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Soothill Nether 
    and Soothill Upper.

Created 1894 out of the parish of Soothill. Abolished 1.4.1925 
    and added to the parish of Dewsbury.

Created 1894 out of the parish of Soothill. Abolished 31.3.1910 
    and divided between the parishes of Batley and Dewsbury.
Abolished 1.4.1925 and added to the parish of Dewsbury.
Abolished 26.3.1896 and added to the parish of Thornhill.
